Vendored Kronos model code
==========================

Source : https://github.com/shiyu-coder/Kronos  (model/kronos.py, model/module.py)
License: MIT (c) the Kronos authors
Paper  : "Kronos: A Foundation Model for the Language of Financial Markets", arXiv:2508.02739

Only the model definition is vendored here (no PyPI package exists). The only
local modification to kronos.py is the import header: the `sys.path` hack and
`from model.module import *` were replaced with a relative `from .module import *`
so the code works as a package. Pre-trained weights are downloaded from the
Hugging Face Hub (NeoQuasar/*) at runtime by app.ml.kronos_loader.
